{"tid":919880,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先係地鐵站有個死廢老亂咁吠","createTime":"2018-11-28T11:24:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T13:44:44.000Z","uid":208516,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"61b89f87811b0f4fd56f59222cec6789e164e805","tid":919880,"uid":208516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:24:05.000Z","msg":"頭先我諗住岀閘嗰陣條死廢老企係度唔岀<br />\n<br />\n咁我咪諗住拍卡岀閘先囉<br />\n<br />\n點知條廢老屌我<br />\n<br />\n話我打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢講話：痴撚線你企係個閘度又唔行咁我咪行先囉<br />\n<br />\n然後佢話：前面有人啊嘛，我要畀人行先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我:你前面撚有人啊on9?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岀咗閘之後佢仲繼續屌<br />\n<br />\n廢老:你真係好冇禮貌！<br />\n<br />\n我:你番屋企食屎啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n廢老:你去死啦！<br />\n<br />\n我:好呀！我想死好耐啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我同佢講你都痴撚線㗎跟住一野撞開佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcac202f640ed465379b24be4d00fffe831715a3","tid":919880,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:27:07.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"553fadb6230be5ba521c025093a63407dd2d1931","tid":919880,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9418ae7eee2b6fed927f4a911fc2a2141676b51","tid":919880,"uid":208711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"打柒佢啦 係我唔忍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b07ab06c74e15c179687acb83cc1a91bef5ecff","tid":919880,"uid":54593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji